  "text": "In this paper, we present an approach for the development of a fuzzy based IR system. The approach provides a new mechanism for constructing and integrating three relevancy profiles: a task profile, a user profile and document profile, into a unified index through the use of relevance feedback and fuzzy rule based summarisation [CITATION_1] .",
